{"tid":1962235,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰空姐改60歲退休？　","createTime":"2020-04-07T10:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T11:03:57.000Z","uid":297241,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d7500a4c8abd11a0f40584cf9ed1e5a57f40d03f","tid":1962235,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:33:56.000Z","msg":"國泰空姐改60歲退休？　<br />\n工會不滿問卷有前設<br />\n<br />\n香港國泰航空現時將空勤人員的退休年齡定於55歲，惟辦公室員工及飛機師的退休年齡，分別為60及65歲，香港空勤人員總工會批評安排屬年齡歧視，國泰近日展開「延長退休年齡至60歲」的員工網上問卷調查，但工會認為網上問卷調查有前設，促請國泰盡快就延長退休年齡與工會展開談判，令空勤人員有選擇退休的自主權。"},{"pid":"8d06297eec15416afaf9bedf4f0f968a99864b11","tid":1962235,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:35:01.000Z","msg":"60歲因住要我地serve番佢轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53f671da97a3607e9842e2c45f2918176e43a08","tid":1962235,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d06297eec15416afaf9bedf4f0f968a99864b11","tid":1962235,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:35:01.000Z","msg":"60歲因住要我地serve番佢轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://loyaltylobby.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/AA-FA-80th.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Floyaltylobby.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F05%2FAA-FA-80th.png&h=4d69a163&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f93378ba047edaa49cd91e8f39c58115127b0bed","tid":1962235,"uid":123053,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:03:57.000Z","msg":"60歲路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}